0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:34:03.000Z","msg":"大sam迫不及待想玩玩了"},{"pid":"36506e2ea3f9c91ca3aa8ccc46664e4d0dbd7f23","tid":850844,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.scribblelive.com/2013/9/2/e1aade48-b367-41c9-ae70-84f544c4e7f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.scribblelive.com%2F2013%2F9%2F2%2Fe1aade48-b367-41c9-ae70-84f544c4e7f2.gif&h=06a99c35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6acd317b20f3a039bf42adc4b49211c2a066ea9","tid":850844,"uid":124292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"黎多次空難"},{"pid":"4194aef3d0fa14fefd5a709429b43bb35959f709","tid":850844,"uid":17473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:36:17.000Z","msg":"踢到咁政治，施丹都唔敢過黎<br />\n成隊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec2f85840b205080cf0c4def2d6725be182e84c","tid":850844,"uid":38583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  降班修煉過吧啦，費sir 果替人走曬之後管理層球員教練都成舊屎咁，"},{"pid":"789ea8bd93427e36db1c901f9cf1119b020bfdef","tid":850844,"uid":34127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2c3c962eac07dc321b2511cd6be4b094ce7252","tid":850844,"uid":131369,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"雲加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}